    <span class="eyebrow">About SARA</span>
    <h1>Unconditional life, since {{ site.founded }}.</h1>
    <p>SARA stands for Society for Animal Rescue &amp; Adoption. What started as a small rescue has grown into one of the largest sanctuaries in the world, with {{ site.animalsInCare }} animals in our care at any given time.</p>
  </div>
