  <div class="container">
    <div class="two-col reverse">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Our Sanctuary</span>
        <h2>Hard work, long hours, real results.</h2>
        <p>Running a sanctuary is rewarding and relentless. It takes a lot of physical and emotional labor, and a great deal of money to feed and care for the animals that come to us.</p>
        <p>Every animal at SARA receives quality food, spay/neuter, protection from external and internal parasites, and excellent veterinary care. No exceptions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="img" style="background: url('/images/barn.webp') center/cover;"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

