      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Our Animals</span>
        <h2>Some we place. Some stay forever.</h2>
        <p>We try to find homes for all of our animals and work extensively with rescues across the US. We've taken in dogs from as far away as the Middle East and Malaysia. Our residents have been featured in Newsweek, Spectrum News, and Texas Lifestyle Magazine.</p>
        <p>But some animals don't fit into a conventional home setting and still deserve a loving, safe environment. Many of the residents here fall into that category and will remain with us as happy permanent residents.</p>
