        <h2>The big red barn works hard.</h2>
        <p>Our big red barn is a multi-purpose building. It provides shelter for some of our aging animals and houses a veterinary room, laundry, bath, and guest quarters.</p>
        <p>You can also book a stay in our cozy upstairs loft with its observation deck. It's perfect for lounging, bird watching, and taking in incredible Texas sunsets. ATV-guided tours are available to get you up close with our animal residents.</p>
        <a href="/visit/" class="btn btn-forest mt-2">Book a Stay</a>
